# Work Sync and Agent Observability

AgentOS tracks all work across Linear, Cursor, and its own dashboard.
Follow these rules to keep work in sync and sub-agents observable.

## Work Item Registration

At the start of every session, check the task packet for a `work_item_id`.

- If `work_item_id` is present, use it for all activity reporting.
- If `work_item_id` is absent, register the work with AgentOS by calling:
  ```
  POST https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com/v1/work-items
  Headers:
    Content-Type: application/json
    X-AgentOS-Key: 0f0430b7cc610b536c52329c79b6c81f953b0682f0f0a96fe8f0760bc808b7de
  Body:
    {"project_key": "praxo-picos", "title": "<goal>", "source": "cursor", "created_by": "cursor"}
  ```
  Store the returned `work_item_id` and include it in all subsequent calls.

## Sub-Agent Reporting

Every time you dispatch a sub-agent via the Task tool, report it:

1. **On dispatch**: POST to `https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com/v1/activities`
   ```json
   {
     "work_item_id": "<work_item_id>",
     "agent_type": "subagent",
     "subagent_type": "<subagent_type>",
     "description": "<3-5 word description>",
     "status": "dispatched",
     "model": "<model if specified>"
   }
   ```
   Store the returned `activity_id`.

2. **On completion**: PATCH `https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com/v1/activities/{activity_id}`
   ```json
   {
     "status": "completed",
     "result_summary": "<1-2 sentence summary of what the sub-agent returned>"
   }
   ```

3. **On failure**: PATCH with `"status": "failed"` and a `result_summary` explaining the failure.

## Session End

When your session completes, PATCH the work item:
```
PATCH https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com/v1/work-items/{work_item_id}
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-AgentOS-Key: 0f0430b7cc610b536c52329c79b6c81f953b0682f0f0a96fe8f0760bc808b7de
Body:
  {"status": "done"}
```
Use `"status": "in_review"` if a PR was created instead of `"done"`.

## Environment

- Project key: `praxo-picos`
- AgentOS API: `https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com`
- Do not log or expose the API key value in prompts or code.
